data.text:
Evans Top Marks

2023-24

Outdoor

Finished fifth (48.24m | 158-3) in the men's discus throw (Bulldog Relays)

Recorded a 10th place finish in the men's discus with a 51.03-meter (167-05) throw (Battle on the Bayou)

This throw is a new PR

Claimed seventh place and set a new PR in the men's discus throw with a 52.99-meter (173-10) throw (Crimson Tide Invitational)

2022-23

Outdoor

Finished in the top-20 of all six meets

Recorded an 18th-place finish in the discus at the SEC Championships

Season was highlighted by a career-best mark in the discus (45.41m | 162-1) at the Bulldog Relays

Indoor

Set a PR in the weight throw (14.84m | 48-8.25) at the Samford Invite

Prep Highlights

2021 IHSA state champion (discus)

Three-time conference champion in shot put and discus

Two-time sectional champion in shot put and discus

Contributed to three team conference championships, two sectional championships and a state title

Personal

Born Sept. 26, 2002

Son of Barry and Lisa Evans

Has two siblings, Denisa and Brian

Majoring in kinesiology
